---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy | ZoningBase"
  description="ZoningBase privacy policy. How we collect, use, and protect your data."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 sm:py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-text-muted text-sm">Last updated: April 2026</p>

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-8 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          ZoningBase collects limited information to operate and improve the service:
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Analytics data:</strong> We use Google Analytics (GA4) to understand how visitors use the site. This includes anonymized page views, session duration, and general geographic region. No personally identifiable information is collected through analytics.</li>
          <li><strong>Contact form submissions:</strong> If you submit a form on ZoningBase, we collect the information you provide (name, email, message) solely to respond to your inquiry.</li>
          <li><strong>Server logs:</strong> Our hosting provider (Cloudflare) may collect standard web server logs including IP addresses, browser type, and request timestamps for security and performance purposes.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          We use collected information to operate, maintain, and improve ZoningBase. We do not sell, rent, or share personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">Cookies</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          ZoningBase uses cookies for analytics (Google Analytics) and essential site functionality. You can control cookie preferences through your browser settings.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Cloudflare:</strong> Hosting, CDN, and security services.</li>
          <li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> Website usage analytics.</li>
          <li><strong>OpenStreetMap:</strong> Map tiles on zone detail pages.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">Data Retention</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          Analytics data is retained according to Google Analytics default retention settings. Contact form submissions are retained only as long as needed to respond to your inquiry.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">Contact</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          For privacy-related questions, contact us via the <a href="/contact/" class="text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700 underline">contact page</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border">
      <a href="/" class="text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700 font-medium text-sm">
        &larr; Back to all states
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
